faq-topviews-false-positive-body1: He nama manakore ēna. Ahakoa he whakapōrearea ngā nama manakore, kāhore e taea te whakakore ēna. Ko tētahi whakatauira, ka mahi tētahi pūmanawa rorohiko aunoa ki te tukua atu tētahi whārangi i ngā wā katoa. Ko tētahi rautaki ki te rapuhia ngā nama manakore te mahi whakataurite: ka whakataurite ngā titiro o ngā rorohiko papa mahi ki te titiro o ngā waea pūkoro. I te nuinga o ngā wā, he nui ngā titiro o ngā waea pūkoro i ngā titiro o ngā rorohiko papa mahi. Mehemea he iti ngā titiro o ngā waea pūkoro, he nama manakore, pea.
